{"title_page": "Carnal Diafragma", "text_new": "{{multiple issues|\n{{notability|Music|date=December 2014}}\n{{unreferenced|date=December 2014}}\n{{Orphan|date=December 2014}}\n}}\n\n{{Infobox musical artist\n| name            = Carnal Diafragma\n| image           =\n| image_size      = \n| landscape       = <!-- yes, if wide image, otherwise leave blank -->\n| alt             = \n| caption         = Members 2017: David, Lukas, Robert, Kino\n| background      = group_or_band\n| alias           = \n| origin          = [[Ostrava]],  {{flag|Czech Republic}}\n| genre           = [[Goregrind]]\n| years_active    = {{start date|1997}}-present\n| label           = Khaaranus Production, Lecter Music Agency, Bizarre Leprous Prod.\n| associated_acts = [[Napalm Death]], [[GUT (band)|GUT]], [[Cock and Ball Torture (band)|Cock and Ball Torture]]\n| current_members = Martin \"Kino\" Va\u0161ek<br />Robert \"Ro\u017ean\" Ro\u017eanski<br />David \"Sabon\" Sn\u011bhota<br />Luk\u00e1\u0161 Jel\u00ednek\n}}\n\n\n'''Carnal Diafragma''' is a [[goregrind]] band from the [[Czech Republic]] formed in 1997 in [[Ostrava]].\n\n==History==\nCarnal Diafragma was formed in [[Ostrava]] in 1997 by Robert Ro\u017eanski - guitar / vocals, Milan Janak - voice and Michal \"Kame\u0148\" Kaminski - battery. The band played [[Noise music|noise]]/[[Grindcore|grind]], and sometimes touching on themes of gender [[Pornogrind]] gradually evolved into more serious [[Goregrind]]. At this time Luk\u00e1\u0161 \"Stezi\" Stejskal - bass joined the band but later came out and in 2000 David \"Sabon\" Snehota - under it replaced. In 2001 Stezi returned and the band recorded their first album \"Preparation of Patients for the Examination\" which was edited by Khaaranus Production. In 2002 the band recorded their MD ''\"Daddy's Steak\"'' and split 7 \"EP with the German band Ulcerrhoea. Then Stezi definitely left the band. In 2006 Carnal Diafragma recorded her second album ''\"Space Symphony Around U\"'' which was edited by Lecter Music Agency and soon became known worldwide mainly thanks to video ''\"Teletrambus\"''. Then Kame\u0148 left the band for personal problems and was replaced by Ond\u0159ej \"Prune\" Pode\u0161va. In 2009 David and Pode left the band and their replacements were Libor \"Porky\" Philipp - drums with brother David Martin \"Sabon\" Snehota - bass. The band recorded their third album ''\"Planet of Children's Heads\"'', Martin left the band and returned David. In 2015 Milan left the band and Kino (BBYB, ex-Cerebral Turbulency) joined the band. That year split CD with Mexican band Fecalizer was released and in February 2017 fourth album called \"Grind Restaurant pana Septika\" was released by Czech label Bizarre Leprous Prod. In June 2017 Libor left the band and Lukas Jelinek (Felisha, ex-Spasm) became a new drummer. Carnal Diafragma has participated in many compilations and split CDs and tapes with various bands. They have played many concerts in the [[Czech Republic]], [[Slovakia]], [[Germany]], [[Austria]], [[Poland]], [[Ukraine]], [[Netherlands]], [[Portugal]], [[Hungary]] and [[Italy]].\n\n==Current Lineup==\n*Robert - guitar, vocals (1997-present)\n*David - bass (2000-present)\n*Kino - vocals (2015-present)\n*Lukas - drums (2017-present)\n\n==Past Members==\n*Stezy - bass (1997-2004)\n*Michal - drums (1997-2006)\n*Milan - vocals (1997-2015)\n*Kamen - drums (2003-2006)\n*Pode - drums (2006-2009)\n*Martin - bass (2009-2012)\n*Libor - drums (2009-2017)\n\n==Discography==\n\n===Albums===\n*2001 - Preparation of the Patients for Examination\n*2006 - Space Symphony Around Us\n*2011 - Planet of Children's Heads\n*2017 - Grind Restaurant pana Septika\n\n===Others===\n*1998 - We cut your head and fuck your neck (demo)\n*1998 - 3-way split w/ Pissed Cunt/Rabies ([[Compact Cassette|cassette]])\n*1999 - Live in Hav\u00ed\u0159ov (live demo)\n*2001 - Comeback of Goregods - Tribute to Regurgitate (compilation CD)\n*2001 - split w/ P.I.T. (cassette)\n*2003 - split w/ Ulcerrhoea (7\"EP)\n*2003 - Amore Mio (6-way split cassette)\n*2003 - Tribute to Gut (compilaci\u00f3n CD)\n*2004 - split w/ Bizarre Embalming (split mini CD)\n*2004 - Daddy's Steak (cassette)\n*2004 - split w/Pulmonary Fibrosis (CD-R)\n*2005 - Hardcore Metal Punk Forever (compilation DVD)\n*2007 - Splatter Fetish - 100 Way Cumpilation\n*2008 - Preparation of the Daddy's Steak (re-edici\u00f3n CD+Daddy's Steak)\n*2015 - Grind Monsters - split w/ Fecalizer (CD)\n\n==External links==\n* [https://www.facebook.com/pages/Carnal-Diafragma-official/136245863107718?fref=ts Perfil de Carnal Diafragma en Facebook]\n* [http://bandzone.cz/carnaldiafragma Perfil de Carnal Diafragma en Bandzone]\n* [http://www.metal-archives.com/bands/Carnal_Diafragma/2441 Carnal Diafragma] en [[Encyclopaedia Metallum]] \n* [http://www.discogs.com/artist/581618-Carnal-Diafragma Carnal Diafragma], [[discogs|Discogs.com]] \n* [http://www.last.fm/music/Carnal+Diafragma Carnal Diafragma], [[Last.fm]]\n* http://morguefanzin.blogspot.cz/2014/02/carnal-diafragma-interview.html\n\n{{Portal|Music}}\n\n[[Category:Czech heavy metal musical groups]]\n[[Category:Grindcore musical groups]]\n[[Category:Goregrind musical groups]]\n", "text_old": "{{multiple issues|\n{{notability|Music|date=December 2014}}\n{{unreferenced|date=December 2014}}\n{{Orphan|date=December 2014}}\n}}\n\n{{Infobox musical artist\n| name            = Carnal Diafragma\n| image           =\n| image_size      = \n| landscape       = <!-- yes, if wide image, otherwise leave blank -->\n| alt             = \n| caption         = Members 2017: David, Lukas, Robert, Kino\n| background      = group_or_band\n| alias           = \n| origin          = [[Ostrava]],  {{flag|Czech Republic}}\n| genre           = [[Goregrind]]\n| years_active    = {{start date|1997}}-present\n| label           = Khaaranus Production, Lecter Music Agency, Bizarre Leprous Prod.\n| associated_acts = [[Napalm Death]], [[GUT (band)|GUT]], [[Cock and Ball Torture (band)|Cock and Ball Torture]]\n| current_members = Martin \"Kino\" Va\u0161ek<br />Robert \"Ro\u017ean\" Ro\u017eanski<br />David \"Sabon\" Sn\u011bhota<br />Luk\u00e1\u0161 Jel\u00ednek\n}}\n\n\n'''Carnal Diafragma''' is a [[goregrind]] band from the [[Czech Republic]] formed in 1997 in [[Ostrava]].\n\n==History==\nCarnal Diafragma was formed in [[Ostrava]] in 1997 by Robert Ro\u017eanski - guitar / vocals, Milan Janak - voice and Michal \"Kame\u0148\" Kaminski - battery. The band played [[Noise music|noise]]/[[Grindcore|grind]], and sometimes touching on themes of gender [[Pornogrind]] gradually evolved into more serious [[Goregrind]]. At this time Luk\u00e1\u0161 \"Stezi\" Stejskal - bass joined the band but later came out and in 2000 David \"Sabon\" Snehota - under it replaced. In 2001 Stezi returned and the band recorded their first album \"Preparation of Patients for the Examination\" which was edited by Khaaranus Production. In 2002 the band recorded their MD ''\"Daddy's Steak\"'' and split 7 \"EP with the German band Ulcerrhoea. Then Stezi definitely left the band. In 2006 Carnal Diafragma recorded her second album ''\"Space Symphony Around U\"'' which was edited by Lecter Music Agency and soon became known worldwide mainly thanks to video ''\"Teletrambus\"''. Then Kame\u0148 left the band for personal problems and was replaced by Ond\u0159ej \"Prune\" Pode\u0161va. In 2009 David and Pode left the band and their replacements were Libor \"Porky\" Philipp - drums with brother David Martin \"Sabon\" Snehota - bass. The band recorded their third album ''\"Planet of Children's Heads\"'', Martin left the band and returned David. In 2015 Milan left the band and Kino (BBYB, ex-Cerebral Turbulency) joined the band. That year split CD with Mexican band Fecalizer was released and in February 2017 fourth album called \"Grind Restaurant pana Septika\" was released by Czech label Bizarre Leprous Prod. In June 2017 Libor left the band and Lukas Jelinek (Felisha, ex-Spasm) became a new drummer. Carnal Diafragma has participated in many compilations and split CDs and tapes with various bands. They have played many concerts in the [[Czech Republic]], [[Slovakia]], [[Germany]], [[Austria]], [[Poland]], [[Ukraine]], [[Netherlands]], [[Portugal]], [[Hungary]] and [[Italy]].\n\n==Current Lineup==\n*Robert - guitar, vocals (1997-present)\n*David - bass (2000-present)\n*Kino - vocals (2015-present)\n*Lukas - drums (2017-present)\n\n==Past Members==\n*Stezy - bass (1997-2004)\n*Michal - drums (1997-2006)\n*Milan - vocals (1997-2015)\n*Kamen - drums (2003-2006)\n*Pode - drums (2006-2009)\n*Martin - bass (2009-2012)\n*Libor - drums (2009-2017)\n\n==Discography==\n\n===Albums===\n*2001 - Preparation of the Patients for Examination\n*2006 - Space Symphony Around Us\n*2011 - Planet of Children\u00b4s Heads\n*2017 - Grind Restaurant pana Septika\n\n===Others===\n*1998 - We cut your head and fuck your neck (demo)\n*1998 - 3-way split w/ Pissed Cunt/Rabies ([[Compact Cassette|cassette]])\n*1999 - Live in Hav\u00ed\u0159ov (live demo)\n*2001 - Comeback of Goregods - Tribute to Regurgitate (compilation CD)\n*2001 - split w/ P.I.T. (cassette)\n*2003 - split w/ Ulcerrhoea (7\"EP)\n*2003 - Amore Mio (6-way split cassette)\n*2003 - Tribute to Gut (compilaci\u00f3n CD)\n*2004 - split w/ Bizarre Embalming (split mini CD)\n*2004 - Daddy\u00b4s Steak (cassette)\n*2004 - split w/Pulmonary Fibrosis (CD-R)\n*2005 - Hardcore Metal Punk Forever (compilation DVD)\n*2007 - Splatter Fetish - 100 Way Cumpilation\n*2008 - Preparation of the Daddy\u00b4s Steak (re-edici\u00f3n CD+Daddy\u00b4s Steak)\n*2015 - Grind Monsters - split w/ Fecalizer (CD)\n\n==External links==\n* [https://www.facebook.com/pages/Carnal-Diafragma-official/136245863107718?fref=ts Perfil de Carnal Diafragma en Facebook]\n* [http://bandzone.cz/carnaldiafragma Perfil de Carnal Diafragma en Bandzone]\n* [http://www.metal-archives.com/bands/Carnal_Diafragma/2441 Carnal Diafragma] en [[Encyclopaedia Metallum]] \n* [